==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Enterprising
<hw>En"ter*pri`sing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having a
disposition for enterprise; characterized by enterprise; resolute,
active or prompt to attempt; <as>as, an <ex>enterprising</ex> man or
firm</as>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>En"ter*pri`sing*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

